										<p>Upon acceptance into the Program, WEBTOON will establish a Net Ad Revenue account ("Account") and related "AD SHARING Tab" for you. Thereafter, your portion of Net Ad Revenue, if any, will be posted to your Account on a monthly basis, and updated in the AD SHARING Tab on the 21st day of the following month. You will not receive an individual email notification indicating that you have received payment of any Net Ad Revenue or that your Account has been updated. </p>
