										<p class="bold">Note! If you cancel your membership in the Ad Revenue Sharing Program or delete your Account at any time in which there is a balance of $10 or more in your Account, WEBTOON will pay you amounts in excess of $10. Any balance reflected in your Account below the applicable threshold of $10 will remain unpaid.</p>
